@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}
<style>
    .redaboutbanner, .blackaboutbanner {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
    }

        .redaboutbanner h2, .blackaboutbanner h2 {
            padding-top:3%;
            color: white; 
            font-weight: bold; 
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .redaboutbanner p, .blackaboutbanner p {
            color: #e3e6e4;
            font-size: 17px;
        }
</style>
<section class="search-wrapper my-3 py-3 pl-4 pl-lg-5 pl-md-5 pr-lg-5 pr-md-5 pr-0" style="border-top: 1px solid #000;">
    <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-between" >
            <div class="pb-5 col-12 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-lg-6 px-0 px-sm-3">
                <div class="pb-4">
                    <h3 class="heading my-4">Overview</h3>
                    <p class="mt-1 mb-4" style="color: #000;">
                        Over the years YRT has evolved to be one of the most reliable and
                        reputable automobile trading companiesheadquartered in Gunma, Japan.
                        YRT was established
                        in the year 2005.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="">
                    <h3 class="heading my-4">YRT Team</h3>
                    <p class="mt-1" style="color: #000;">
                        The YRT team is made up of the
                        most technically experienced sales staff who guide the customers as per their
                        requirements. YRT team provides you with the service of buying cars through some of the most
                        complicated and vast Auctions & Dealer stocks in Japan. The YRT team has been trained to
                        find the exact car that our clients have been searching for. We ensure that our clients feel
                        heard and do not settle for anything less than their desires. 

                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-sm-12 col-lg-6 px-0 px-sm-3">
                <img src="../images/about-banner.png" class="d-block mx-auto" alt="">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-between pt-4">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-lg-6 px-0 pr-2 position-relative">
            <img src="../images/red-about-banner.png" style="width: 100%;object-fit: cover;" alt="">
            <div class="redaboutbanner ">
                <h2 class="missionheading pt-5">Vision Statement</h2>
                <p class="missionpara">
                   Striving to set the global standard for quality
                    and reliability in Japanese used car exports, providing customers worldwide with seamless
                        access to their ideal vehicles from Japanese auctions.
                    
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-lg-6 px-0 pl-2 position-relative">
            <img src="../images/black-about-banner.png" style="width: 100%;object-fit: cover;" alt="">
            <div class="blackaboutbanner ">
                <h2 class="missionheading pt-5">Mission Statement</h2>
                <p class="missionpara">
                   To deliver exceptional Japanese vehicles
                    worldwide, connecting our customers with the finest quality through precision, trust,
                        and expert navigation of Japanese auctions.
                    
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>


            <div class="w-100 d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-between pt-5">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mx-auto">
                    <div class="valuescontainer">
                        <img src="../images/values.svg" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="heading my-4 ml-2">YRT Values</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="missionpara mb-0 mx-auto pt-3 text-center" style="color: #000; font-size: 15px;">
                    At YRT,
                    we have strict rules and regulations set in place at each step to ensure the transparency
                    and accuracy of the information that we provide to our clients. All your vehicles are
                    thoroughly examined before bidding and at each step of the process. The client is regularly
                    updated on the exact condition and location of their vehicles.
                </p>
                <p class="missionpara mb-0 mx-auto text-center" style="color: #000; font-size: 15px;">
                    If you are
                    thinking about purchasing a Japanese used car feel free to reach out to our experts,
                    who are available 24/7, in the YRT team for free guidance. <a asp-area="Customer" asp-controller="Contact" asp-action="Index">
                        <strong>
                            <span class="redCol">(Contact Us!)</span>
                        </strong>
                    </a>
                    .Our customers from all around the globe leave the most heartwarming reviews <a asp-area="Customer" asp-controller="Testimonials" asp-action="Index">
                        <strong>
                            <span class="redCol">(Reviews).</span>
                        </strong>
                    </a>
                    . We are always ready to welcome our new customers, whether are dealers or end
                    users. Our motive is to provide the best services to each client and aim for their satisfaction.
                </p>
                <p class="missionpara mb-0 mx-auto pt-3 pb-5 text-center" style="color: #000; font-size: 15px;">
                    YRT also operates a large sales centre in Chile, featuring a wide selection of both Japanese and
                    Korean vehicles. All the cars available are owned by YRT, and the centre has the capacity to
                    showcase over 70 cars for customers to view. YRT’s dedicated sales team is available to assist
                    customers during both day and night markets.
                </p>
            </div>



